snippet.title: Archipelago: Island Survival. Official Trailer.
snippet.description:
After a shipwreck, you find yourself on an archipelago of islands. You need to travel between the islands and survive.

The free demo version is already available on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2886220/Archipelago_Island_Survival
